source.name: Federal Aircraft Cost and Utilization Data
source.description: Federal aviation data is submitted quarterly to the Federal Aviation Interactive Reporting System (FAIRS) IT application. This is a GSA system which is a secure, web-based application. The report summarizes the annual aviation cost and utilization information submitted by the thirteen agencies that own or operate aircraft as part of their mission.
